org.sql: SELECT DISTINCT notes.* FROM notes INNER JOIN note_comments ON note_comments.note_id = notes.id AND note_comments.visible = "$1" LEFT OUTER JOIN users ON users.id = note_comments.author_id AND (users.status IN ("$2", "$3") OR users.status IS NULL) WHERE (notes.status = "$4" OR notes.status = "$5" AND notes.closed_at > '2022-08-22 21:22:00.539509') AND note_comments.author_id = "$6" ORDER BY updated_at DESC LIMIT "$7"
